              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17876709630564636198">Loved everything about this book! The writing is lyrical, and I really appreciated that the narrator is the uncle, rather than the girl. It’s more authentic. And I loved the parts from the perspectives of the whales. Excellent! Definitely worth reading! 5 stars</span>

          </span>
